Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.75,0:00:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落葉先生又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下明天早晨的打掃要辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.60,0:00:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊好像也很辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.25,0:00:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.43,0:00:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老師...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我難道不能做些什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.59,0:00:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起出門了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.63,0:00:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 去參加她們學校義賣會的預備會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義賣會?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.38,0:00:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起拿東西來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.38,0:01:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把它們賣掉 得到的錢用在學校上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個!

Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.43,0:01:19.67,logo,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}KTXP&SD字幕組
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:15.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}どうすうればいいんだっけ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:15.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}該怎麼辦才好來著?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:19.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}あたりまえのことっていつも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:19.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}理所當然的事情總是這麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.70,0:01:23.63,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}難しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.70,0:01:23.63,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}紛繁複雜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.04,0:01:26.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}嬉しいとき笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.04,0:01:26.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}只是想開心的時候就笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.01,0:01:31.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}好きなときに歌いたいだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.01,0:01:31.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}想唱歌的時候就唱歌而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.78,0:01:34.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.78,0:01:34.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.21,0:01:39.71,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}いつか願いは叶うと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.21,0:01:39.71,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}常說願望總會實現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:46.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}でもいつかってどれくらい待ちきれないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:46.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可是總會到底要多久　已經等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.32,0:01:49.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}１ ２ ３　の合図で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.32,0:01:49.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}看好1 2 3的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.27,0:01:52.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}両手　ひろげて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.27,0:01:52.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}張開雙臂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.14,0:01:58.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}全身に　光をあつめて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.14,0:01:58.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}让全身充满光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.17,0:02:00.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}どこに　あるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.17,0:02:00.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}告訴我在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:04.19,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}教えて私にできること
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:04.19,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:07.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}目一杯　傷ついて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:07.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}傷得滿目瘡痍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:09.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}精一杯　走って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:09.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}跑的精疲力盡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:14.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}何十回　転んで泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:14.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}幾十次摔倒哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.60,0:02:16.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}それでもまた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.60,0:02:16.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}即使是這樣還
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.27,0:02:20.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あきれるくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.27,0:02:20.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}難以置信地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.44,0:02:25.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}明日を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.44,0:02:25.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}相信著明天

