Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}[...迷之生命體.]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.11,0:02:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦義賣會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老師 我們來辦義賣會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.05,0:02:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣掉許多各種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.95,0:02:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把得到的錢還給討債的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:03:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把錢還清 就不用搬走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.69,0:03:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 好嗎 義賣會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那麼容易就能還得了的話 早就還了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在比較大的學校辦也許還能有些收入
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.39,0:03:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種沒幾個學生的保育園
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算辦義賣會又能有多少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦了也白辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我自顧自地激動起來...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去打掃院子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果全力以赴地辦起義賣會來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果真的不行的話 最可憐的還是小鳩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白因為這個你才想讓她放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.19,0:04:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那種說法可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話總是不顧忌別人的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就真成壞心眼了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只顧自己興高采烈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生和清花老師都對我無話可說了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好傻啊 我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 傻是傻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 那股拚命勁我覺得倒不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:04:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別摟著我 肉麻死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來辦吧 義賣會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義賣會?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把家裡不要的東西或者自己製作的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.77,0:05:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶到保育園來賣掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是開店遊戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.61,0:05:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想開炒麵店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是個好主意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在聯絡簿上把詳細情形寫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿回去給家裡人看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們開什麼樣的店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩又打起精神來了真是太好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我沒什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BYEBYE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老師 明天再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.13,0:05:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼哼哼~義賣會~哼哼哼哼哼哼哼~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.35,0:06:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(艾草保育園 義賣會)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小汪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得對不起狗和貓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都沒說錯所以沒法反駁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是小鳩畫的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫得真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛的鴨子和綿羊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉強自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.21,0:06:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老師才是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生 也會像那樣笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(迷之生命體)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那先失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.52,0:07:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然做這種小孩子一樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是很喜歡小鳩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本君也是 那個人也是 都這麼不坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小鳩 今天辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義賣會的準備 明天再繼續做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是清花老師的丈夫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得您曾經為您丈夫訂過生日蛋糕的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說那個人也不坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.82,0:08:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個什麼樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.34,0:08:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個謎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和土鳩的畫比起來還不算是謎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是放晴娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放晴娃娃?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個呢 是為了求晴天做來掛起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰拿來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.27,0:08:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是奈緒美做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:08:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做的放晴娃娃很有效的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠足的時候 去游泳池的時候都天晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害的放晴娃娃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能賣出去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能的 我也會做些東西帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺在一起賣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼給大家帶來的東西貼上價簽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能賣出去很多放晴娃娃的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保育園就不會沒掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個呢 我媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快要生小寶寶了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽說她雖然從這個月開始休假了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:10:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等小寶寶長大一點以後 又要開始工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.29,0:10:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候想把小寶寶再托給艾草保育園
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢 因為我是姐姐 會來保育園接他的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣每天都能見到清花老師和小鳩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當姐姐的奈緒美 我也每天都想見到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.38,0:10:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(艾草保育園義賣會)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:11:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經非常晚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是艾草保育園的人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音 是之前接電話的小姑娘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.77,0:11:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討債的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把保育園砸爛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還款期限不能延後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.75,0:11:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...電話裡的...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.93,0:11:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加班?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 是貼義賣會的海報去了才這麼晚的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是壞人 我才不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有趣的小姑娘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打電話的時候我就這麼覺得了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幫我告訴清花了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還款期限不能延後的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把今天我來了的事也幫我告訴她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說期限一到 我就會把保育園砸爛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有小孩在也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不想有人受傷 就趕緊搬走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說砸爛保育園 是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然說有小孩在也一樣 真是過分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長著一張溫和的臉 可是卻讓人覺得害怕 那個男人...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人?什麼樣的男人?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.53,0:13:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐...籐本先生 你在聽著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你讓我聽到的 真是大聲的自言自語呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是自言自語...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個什麼樣男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒問他名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.22,0:13:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個笑瞇瞇的...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還對清花老師直呼清花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沖浦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識他嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.25,0:13:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老師碰見那傢伙了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒...沒有 他跟我說完話就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:14:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙來過的事 不要告訴清花老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.81,0:14:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要多說 照做就是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把清花老師弄哭的話 饒不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 不要再讓清花老師見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫沖浦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跟清花老師是什麼關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.18,0:14:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很清楚了嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.76,0:14:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花那傢伙跟那個男人結婚了所以同姓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.97,0:14:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後那傢伙對清花直呼其名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.21,0:14:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒~~?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說那個人就是清花老師的丈夫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:15:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼為什麼想要把保育園砸爛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.27,0:15:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是不要對這件事插手太多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 還有該做的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果[瓶]不能裝滿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能去你想去的地方了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我很擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 從剛開始就一直在縫什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吉祥物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用千歲小姐給的布縫的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是企鵝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是兔子先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.52,0:15:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是耳朵啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆 不管它是企鵝還是兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.17,0:16:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓義賣會成功
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還打算量產啊 那個迷之物品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.14,0:16:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連五百祗先生都和籐本先生說一樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(艾草保育園義賣會場)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天陰沉沉的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.97,0:16:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 一定會放晴的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.37,0:16:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿肯定能賣出去的東西過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一整天都加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放晴娃娃一定會讓天氣好起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:16:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 可不要摔倒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡邊有飲料的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會摔倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會摔倒的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不會就是不會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人感情真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊 是籐本君從打工的地方拿來的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還不是摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.06,0:17:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太忘我了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩果然還是摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不來呢 客人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明大家一起貼了海報的說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽們可能會來的稍微晚一些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會有其他的客人來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會就這樣一個人都不來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都因為我提議辦什麼義賣會才...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千歲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.49,0:19:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩告訴我們以後 相當期待呢 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來份炒麵如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.01,0:19:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰咖啡也有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要熱咖啡也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你能來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.81,0:19:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千世和千帆也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.99,0:19:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天看海報都沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還擔心是不是中止了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是那傢伙幹的?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去和大家說義賣會沒有中止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在去說已經太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.65,0:19:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會晚 說不定會有人來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算來了 像這樣規模的義賣會...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 哪怕一個人也好我也希望多些人來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 因為
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大家努力辦的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.44,0:20:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大家一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.86,0:20:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本先生也是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個好孩子 小鳩小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.81,0:20:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐本君?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說去叫人了嘛 我去準備咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.28,0:20:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是很坦率但也是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雞?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芒果?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是沒有人來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.30,0:20:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨也停了 太陽也都出來了的說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.22,0:20:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.84,0:21:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義賣會是在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小鳩小姐通知我來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.31,0:21:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 是這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.57,0:21:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說這裡有開義賣會?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼稀罕物件嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.61,0:21:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.16,0:21:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱鬧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.63,0:21:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.93,0:21:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小鳩告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.96,0:21:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩呢?還沒回來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我一杯冰咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.44,0:21:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清和老師 一份冰咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.94,0:21:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位元氣十足的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.90,0:21:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊跑一邊大聲喊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.72,0:22:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在艾草保育園有義賣會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.60,0:22:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}有義賣會~
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.75,0:22:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看她那麼努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忍不住說 是嗎 等下我就去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.11,0:22:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就握著我的手不停地揮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.84,0:22:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以想像呢 確實像小鳩的作風
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.48,0:22:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.48,0:22:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.46,0:22:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉來的晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.19,0:22:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義賣會來了好多客人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.82,0:22:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.75,0:22:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣轉好了真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.48,0:22:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在艾草保育園有義賣會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請各位務必賞光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.54,0:22:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在艾草保育園有義賣會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.74,0:22:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請各位務必賞光

Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.95,0:24:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}下一話[...謎之生命體.2號.]

Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.78,0:23:07.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}人はみな飛んでみたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.59,0:23:14.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}重力に騙されてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.04,0:23:22.95,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}誰もほんとは飛べるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.10,0:23:31.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あの子があんなに悲しそうなのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.37,0:23:42.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}自分の影をどこかに忘れてきちゃったからかも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.65,0:23:44.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}それなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.28,0:23:49.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}ありがとうって　君に言えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.48,0:23:53.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}ありがとうって　君が笑えば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.51,0:24:00.70,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}いったりきたり　嬉しくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.07,0:24:05.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}君が幸せになる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.68,0:24:09.87,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}心配なんていらないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.04,0:24:14.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.74,0:24:27.04,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}嬉しくても涙が出るなんて不思議だ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.78,0:23:07.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}明明人們都是那麼想飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.59,0:23:14.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}只不過被重力所欺騙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.04,0:23:22.95,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}其實誰都可以在天上翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.10,0:23:31.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}那個孩子為什麼如此悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.37,0:23:42.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}也許是把自己的影子忘在了哪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.65,0:23:44.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}是那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.28,0:23:49.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如果能對你說 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.48,0:23:53.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如果能看見你的笑容 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.51,0:24:00.70,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}來來往往中 變得愉悅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.07,0:24:05.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你一定能變得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.68,0:24:09.87,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}不需要擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.04,0:24:14.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}因為我們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.74,0:24:27.04,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}喜極而泣總是那麼不可思議
